metadata.name: PLANT DREAM #005
metadata.description: Plant Dreams is a series that came about when i started to try to think what my character "plant" would dream about. I compilled hundreds and hundreds of photos of stuff related to plants such as water/cells/dirt/sunlight, I uploaded these to an AI and trained it until i got to a point where i liked the images it was producing. These are all digital paintings that are inspired by these AI images of my "plant dreams". These, just like powerful dreams only come about every now and then, so I will keep adding to this collection as time goes by.
